BismiIllah

This App, with simple functions, is made with the three layer architecture.
This architecture consist of a Business Logic, DataAccess and DTO (Data Transfer Object)

The database is made with Entity Framework (EF), that is a framework used to .NET applications. EF is used to work with relational data without focusing on the database tables and columns. Migration is used in this App. 

The API is a ASP.NET Core Web API, that communicates with the backend through the layers. 